46
00:03:36,050 --> 00:03:38,890
Hey, come on. Sit down and
talk with me for a second, okay?

47
00:03:40,890 --> 00:03:42,760
Hey, you, get over here.

48
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:03,050
Lightning Man, help!
Please, I'm begging you!

49
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:05,050
What's wrong, mister?

50
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:09,220
I'm dying of curiosity.

51
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:15,530
