Man, and he'll help you.

52
00:04:17,530 --> 00:04:19,430
You know, back at Sky Park...

53
00:04:21,170 --> 00:04:22,600
Sky Park?

54
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:26,540
You know, where we first met.
When you chased after that doggy.

55
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:29,870
- The doggy.
- Yes, the doggy.

56
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:32,840
Do you remember being me back then?

57
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:36,810
You were running all over the place
on my legs and talking with my mouth.

58
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:41,090
- Yes! It was super fun.
- It was, right?

59
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:45,220
But the thing is, I don't
remember any of it.

60
00:04:45,490 --> 00:04:47,860
So I was hoping you could
tell me what happened.

61
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:52,660
What did you say to that lady back then?

62
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:58,840
- The lady?
- Yes. The one who was with me.

63
00:04:59,370 --> 00:05:00,570
The lady...

64
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,110
Doggy!

65
00:05:04,210 --> 00:05:05,480
Gosh, you're so cute.

66
00:05:06,210 --> 00:05:09,810
