doing, just touching him like that?

67
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,850
Can't you see you're scaring my baby?

68
00:05:13,050 --> 00:05:14,250
Did that scare you?

69
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,650
That lady.

70
00:05:17,590 --> 00:05:19,090
She was really scary.

71
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:22,130
She got mad and glared at me.

72
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:26,800
What? She got mad and glared at you?

73
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,440
I blew it.

74
00:05:34,970 --> 00:05:36,070
I totally blew it.

75
00:05:37,110 --> 00:05:39,140
- I'm done for.
- Want some more?

76
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,710
Eat up now. Okay?

77
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:46,050
- You're up?
- Good morning.

78
00:05:50,460 --> 00:05:52,790
- I'm heading out.
- What about breakfast?

79
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:55,090
I'm not hungry.

80
