88
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:23,150
What?

89
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:29,130
He's the son of a friend of mine.
It's nothing you need to worry about.

90
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:33,230
Who said I cared? I only
care about Woo Jin anyway.

91
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:36,130
And who's Woo Jin?

92
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,800
