93
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:44,310
- What? Mother, you know him?
- Of course I do.

94
00:06:44,610 --> 00:06:46,840
Sure. He's a handsome
kid, cute as a button.

95
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:49,180
